rem quantum ram
rem 8/23/2017

do Examine Ram
 [
  ifitemin quantum ram,INV
   [
    ifin Hosaka North
     [
      print Not here, if someone saw you you'd be caught for sure.
     |
      ifin Hosaka Junction
       [
        print Not here, if someone saw you you'd be caught for sure.
       |
        ifin Hosaka Lobby
         [
          print Not here, if someone saw you you'd be caught for sure.
         |
          ifin Outside Hosaka
           [
            print Not here, if someone saw you you'd be caught for sure.
           |
            ifin Mei Ho Cafe
             [
              print You don't need to pull it out here, you need to slip it to your contact.
             |
              print The small chip lies dormant. It's safe. You don't need to pull it out here.
             ]
           ]
         ]
       ]
     ]
   |
    ifflag simulator off
     [
      print The chip is quiet, but radiating with a little heat.
     |
      print The chip hums with life inside the reality simulator, glowing as it goes
      print through quantum flux.
     ]
   ]
 ]

ifitemin quantum ram,INV
 [|
  do Take Ram
   [
    ifflag simulator off
     [
      print You carefully pull the ram out, uncertin of the quantum state. Hopefully
      print nothing is damaged for your employer.
      move quantum ram,ACTROOM,INV
      setflag have ram
     |
      print The reality simulator is on. Pulling out the ram would destroy the quantum 
      print state.
     ]
   ]
 ]

ifin Mei Ho Cafe
 [
  do Give Contact Ram
   [
    print You hand over the ram to your contact from the Black Net.
    print
    print "Looks like you're rich. The sticks are all there. I'm not going to be a 
    print Mr. Who. Thank you for your service."
    print
    print
    print He walks away leaving you with a bag full of unregistered sticks of new yen.
    print
    printvar It took you, time, turns to complete that run.
    dead
   ]
 |]




